366
00:40:23,090 --> 00:40:25,580
Ho trovato questo da mettermi addosso.

367
00:40:26,600 --> 00:40:28,640
Va bene?

368
00:40:31,100 --> 00:40:33,470
E la divisa della casa.

369
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:44,600
